<p><a name="Literature" id="Literature"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Pipilotti_Rist&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Literature">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Literature</span></h2>
<p><a name="Publications" id="Publications"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Pipilotti_Rist&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Publications">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Publications</span></h3>
<ul>
<li>1998 - <i>Himalaya, Pipilotti Rist 50 kg,</i> incl. CD <i>we can't</i>. Oktagon Verlag: Cologne. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3896110721" class="internal">ISBN 3-89611-072-1</a></li>
<li>1998 - <i>Remake of the Weekend.</i> incl.. CD. Oktagon: Cologne. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3896110462" class="internal">ISBN 3-89611-046-2</a></li>
